            <p>Hi, I'm Tyler.</p>
            <p>I built this AI & LLM News Aggregator because the field moves ridiculously fast—one day it's a new model, the next it's rewriting how we think about intelligence. Sifting through dozens of sources was eating my time, so I made this simple spot to pull the best updates into one clean feed.</p>
            <p>No ads. No noise. Just the latest from the labs and researchers pushing things forward.</p>
